Forsyth et al., Respondents, v. Hannan, Appellant. (Supreme Court, General Term, Fifth Department. June 22, 1889.) Appeal from county court, Monroe county.

Argued before Barker, P. J., and Dwight and Macomber, JJ.

Ho opinion. Judgment affirmed on opinion of the late county judge, John S. Morgan.
